HotApp International, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:34 AM ET
Software

Company Overview of HotApp International, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
HotApp International, Inc. develops mobile applications for instant messaging and ecommerce worldwide. The company offers HotApp, a community communications ecosystem software application for users to connect with local and global communities. Its software application provides messaging and calling services, including text, photo, and audio for HotApp users. The company is based in Bethesda, Maryland. HotApp International, Inc. is a subsidiary of Singapore eDevelopment Limited.


4800 Montgomery LaneSuite 210Bethesda, MD 20814United States17 Employees



Phone: 301-971-3940

hotappinternational.com







Key Executives for HotApp International, Inc.




